edu.jhu.rebar.accumulo

Class AccumuloBackedGraph

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.jhu.rebar.accumulo.AccumuloBackedStagedDataCollection
      • edu.jhu.rebar.accumulo.AccumuloBackedGraph
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Graph, StagedDataCollection

    public class AccumuloBackedGraph
extends AccumuloBackedStagedDataCollection
implements Graph
    Accumulo-backed implementation of the Graph interface. This class should not be directly instantiated; use Graph.Factory.getGraph() instead. The accumulo table that backs each Graph can contain the following cells: 
       RowId    ColFam        ColQual          Value
 --------- ------------- -------------- -----------------------
  edgeId    S+stage       target_uuid       protobuf
  edgeId    N+stage       nbr_uuid
